---Audio API---


How to make play Audio from your Website using a MP3 audio 

This could be used for your website project.


Students will learn how to make HTML buttons that will be interactable using HTML They will be 3 buttons  a PLAY, PAUSE, and STOP. 

Then you will use JavaScript to add logic to these HTML button Elements. 

Things that will need. 

MP3 file 
Visual Studio Code / There is an extension called LiveServer that you can use to create your own server form your computer to be able to see your website that you are making. 

This will be shown during class 
